Context
The MSS live trading bot is complete and running on MT5. The user wants to build a full-featured web trading platform for a small group (friends/team). Requirements gathered over 3 rounds of Q&A:

Architecture: Next.js frontend + Python FastAPI backend (web app)
Brokers: API-first (Oanda, Coinbase first), MT5 bridge + Tradovate later
Backtest: Tick-level simulation, CSV upload initially, later market data APIs
Charts: TradingView Lightweight Charts, later Polygon/Databento MCP for live data
Optimization: Bayesian (Optuna) + Genetic (DEAP) hybrid
ML: Progressive — param optimization → signal prediction → full ML strategies
Strategy Builder: Form-based configuration (dropdowns, condition rows)
Knowledge: All sources (manual, AI-generated, external links, community) + quizzes
Deployment: Local only for now
Timeline: Ongoing / no deadline


